  .info-intro
    %p A joystick is an input device consisting of a stick that pivots on a base and reports its angle or direction to the device it is controlling.
    %p You can use Cylon.js with an Xbox 360 game controller. The goal is to also support any other joysticks and game controllers that are HID devices.
